creator: UniTicker
descriptionHtml:
TickerChart Live is an application for watching real-time information of Middle East Stock Markets. It is a simple to use app that provides ultra low latency data.

Key Features:
- Fast and simple market watch.
- Market liquidity and money flow.
- Real-time charts.
- Technical Analysis tools.
- Market Depth.
- Market Scope (special tool).
- Market Movers.
- Market Big Trades.
- Market Announcements.

The application currently supports Saudi Arabia, Dubai, Qatar and Kuwait Stock Markets.
